info.author: Entropica Labs
info.name: openqaoa
info.summary: OpenQAOA is a python open-source multi-backend Software Development Kit to create, customise and execute the Quantum Approximate Optimisation Algorithm (QAOA) on Noisy Intermediate-Scale Quantum (NISQ) devices, and simulators
